### signup

POST http://localhost:8000/api/signup HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "tilu",
    "email": "tilu@ppms.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Login

POST http://localhost:8000/api/signin HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "tilu",
    "password": "password"
}

### forgot password

POST http://localhost:8000/api/forgot-password HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "",
}

### reset password

POST http://localhost:8000/api/reset-password HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "",
    "newPassword": "",
    "resetString": ""
}

### logout

DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/signout HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### Access the admin panel after authentication (for testing purposes)

GET http://localhost:8000/api/admin-panel